headline: Valmark Financial Group Honored with "Small but Mighty" Award and Named a Top 100 Internship Program in the U.S.
summary: AKRON, Ohio, August 14, 2025--Valmark Financial Group is proud to announce it has been awarded the "Small but Mighty" Award, a distinction celebrating high-impact internship programs led by companies with fewer than 1,000 employees. The award, given by talent acquisition platform Yello in partnership with WayUp, honors organizations that deliver an outsized impact despite their smaller size, recognizing Valmark’s ability to provide exceptional intern experiences and professional development.
